attacks.name: Roar
attacks.effect: Your opponent switches his or her Active Pokémon with 1 of his or her Benched Pokémon.

attacks.name: Ember
attacks.effect: Flip a coin. If tails, discard a Fire Energy attached to this Pokémon.

attacks.name: Epic Splash
attacks.effect: Flip 2 coins. If either of them is tails, this attack does nothing.

attacks.name: Fury Strikes
attacks.effect: Flip 3 coins. This attack does 10 damage times the number of heads.

attacks.name: Tail Whip
attacks.effect: Flip a coin. If heads, the Defending Pokémon can’t attack during your opponent’s next turn.

attacks.name: Heartfelt Song
attacks.effect: Discard a Darkness Energy attached to your opponent’s Active Pokémon.

attacks.name: Nuzzle
attacks.effect: Flip a coin. If heads, your opponent’s Active Pokémon is now Paralyzed.

attacks.name: Act Tough
attacks.effect: If this Pokémon has any Darkness Energy attached to it, this attack does 20 more damage.

attacks.name: Lunge
attacks.effect: Flip a coin. If tails, this attack does nothing.
